Introduction

Park Soo Bin is the Main Vocalist of the girl group Cosmic Girls under Starship Entertainment. She's also part of the sub-unit 'Sweet'. Soobin is considered as the Happy Virus of the group and she represents the Virgo sign in the groups concept.

She debuted as a member of the group on February 25, 2016 with their first mini album Would You Like? and later debuted in their first unit WJSN Chocome on October 7, 2020 with the single album "Hmph!".

On May 9, 2023, she debuted as a member of the virtual project group FE:VERSE under the name KimSerena.
